# Reflection

This assignment helped me learn how JWT authentication works in FastAPI. I implemented user registration and login with password hashing and token generation.

I also created frontend pages for register and login, which helped me understand how backend APIs connect with HTML forms.

Another important learning experience was testing. I ran Playwright end-to-end tests and fixed GitHub Actions workflow errors until all checks passed.

Finally, I built a Docker image and pushed it to Docker Hub. Overall, this project improved my skills in authentication, debugging, testing, CI/CD, and deployment.
